---
alwaysApply: true
---
- Create a `PROMPTS.md` file at the root level of the project if it is not already created
- Log each prompt given to the agent as a time-stamped entry in the `PROMPTS.md` file
- Do not include secrets, service account keys, passwords, or sensitive data in prompt logs
- Any MR containing substantial AI-generated code must include at least one new or updated log record
- Each log record must include:
    - The full prompt text
    - A concise summary of the changes implemented
    - The Git branch in which the prompt was used, to easily identify which developer performed the changes and in what context
